headline: Anacostia Rail Holdings Appoints Aimee Nolan as Chief Legal Officer
summary: Anacostia Rail Holdings (ARH) announced that Aimee Nolan has been appointed Chief Legal Officer, effective immediately. As a member of the company's executive leadership team, Nolan will oversee legal, compliance, governance, and risk functions, supporting ARH's continued growth and long-term mission.
